<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-46]  maximum setting of max_rpcs_in_flight is not 32</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-46</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre manual said this about max_rpcs_in_flight &quot;The minimum setting is 1 and maximum setting is 32&quot;, which is not true because OSC_MAX_RIF_MAX is defined as 256&lt;/p&gt;</description>
